text: Good Naan varieties and dal. Veg Biryani was just abt ok. Bring the only Indian joint in Tuas area, you can go there once in a while...
Very irregular in taking orders. 1 person said food available another said unavailable. Then make people wait very long after makinbg order.
Best Indian restaurant in Tuas. Quality and taste is excellent.
Food is good if you like chapati in Singapore
No fixed price for the dishes as it depends on the person who serves us.
